# Memory Index

## Global User Memory (Six-Domain Model)

Based on the Synthius-Mem paper (arXiv:2604.11563). Load index on session start, retrieve domains on demand.

- [Preferences](domains/03-preferences/_index.md) — Interaction style, habits, decision preferences
- [Biography](domains/01-biography/_index.md) — Identity, roles, background
- [Experiences](domains/02-experiences/_index.md) — Important events and milestones
- [Social Circle](domains/04-social-circle/_index.md) — Team, collaborators, relationships
- [Work](domains/05-work/_index.md) — Projects, skills, tools
- [Psychometrics](domains/06-psychometrics/_index.md) — Thinking patterns and cognitive frameworks

## Project Memory (per-project, isolated)

_No project memories yet. When you start a project, its memory will be created here._
